com.OODPAssn1

Class ConsoleUI

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.OODPAssn1.ConsoleUI
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UserInterface

    public class ConsoleUI
extends java.lang.Object
implements UserInterface
    The ConsoleUI is the front end of the STARS application. No data is handled in this Class.
    Instead, user inputs are sent to the STARS class for processing.
